Package: arbalist
Title: Bringing ArchR to Bioconductor
Version: 0.1.30
Date: 2025-03-11
Description: 
    Implements the core algorithms inside ArchR using C++ bindings to 
    DelayedArrays, in preparation for submission to Bioconductor.
